st find a way to tame this wild animal-like Zord before it destroys everything.\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Beast Morphers (season 2)\n |EpisodeNumber=906\n |EpisodeNumber2=8\n | LineColor=191970\n | Title=Secret Struggle\n | DirectedBy= Oliver Driver\n | WrittenBy= [[Tom Furniss]], Alwyn Dale & Becca Barnes\n | OriginalAirDate={{start date|2020|04|25}}\n | Viewers=\n |ShortSummary= Steel learns that Nate and Zoey have feelings for each other and tries to bring them together, despite the strict Grid Battleforce rules that forbid relationships between Rangers.But Nate and Zoey wereare having a great sex. The wereare doing porn.\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Beast Morphers (season 2)\n |EpisodeNumber=918\n |EpisodeNumber2= Special\n | LineColor=191970\n | Title= Boxed In\n | DirectedBy=Oliver Driver\n | WrittenBy=Alwyn Dale & Becca Barnes, James Collins, Cameron Dixon\nand Maiya Thompson\n | OriginalAirDate={{start date|2020|04|18}}\n | Viewers=0.41<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-saturday-cable-originals-network-finals-4-18-2020.html|title=Top 150 Saturday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 4.18.2020|work=[[Showbuzz Daily]]|author=[[Mitch Metcalf]]|date=April 21, 2020|access-date=Apr 21, 2020}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary= The Pan Global Games arrive in Coral Harbor, but Ranger duties prevent the teens from attending any events.\n}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Power Rangers}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Power Rangers Beast Morphers Episodes, List Of}}\n[[Category:Power Rangers episodes|Beast Morphers]]\n[[Category:Lists of American science fiction television series episodes]]\n[[Category:Lists of American children's television series episodes]]\n[[Category:Lists of Nickelodeon television series episodes]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox television season\n| season_number        = Power Rangers Season 28\n| bgcolour             = #191970\n| image                = \n| image_alt            = \n| caption              = Pow