{"title_page": "Houdini (KSI song)", "text_new": "{{short description|2020 single by KSI featuring Swarmz and Tion Wayne}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date = April 2020}}\n{{Use British English|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = Houdini\n| cover      = KSI Houdini Cover.jpeg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]] featuring Swarmz and Tion Wayne\n| album      = Dissimulation\n| released   = 24 April 2020\n| format=\n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = 2020\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[British hip hop]]\n| length     = 2:49\n| label      =\n* [[RBC Records|RBC]]\n* [[BMG Rights Management|BMG]]\n| writer     =\n* [[KSI (entertainer)|Olajide Olatunji]]\n* Brandon Scott\n* Dennis Odunwo\n* Emmanuel Isong\n* Aj\n* Jacob Mason<ref name=autogenerated1 />\n| producer   =\n* Aj\n* Jacob<ref name=autogenerated1 />\n| chronology = [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]]\n| prev_title = [[Poppin]]\n| prev_year  = 2020\n| next_title =\n| next_year  =\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = Swarmz\n | type       = Singles\n | prev_title = Mojo Jojo\n | prev_year  = 2019\n | title      = Houdini\n | year       = 2020\n | next_title = \n | next_year  = \n}}\n{{Extra chronology\n | artist     = Tion Wayne\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = 4AM\n | prev_year  = 2020\n | title      = Houdini\n | year       = 2020\n | next_title = \n | next_year  = \n}}{{External music video|{{YouTube|0iOSVD1fitU|\"Houdini\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Houdini'''\" is a song by British YouTube personality and rapper [[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]], featuring British singer Swarmz and British rapper Tion Wayne.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://teneightymagazine.com/2020/04/23/ksi-releases-new-track-houdini/|title=KSI Releases New Track \u2018Houdini\u2019|last=|first=|date=2020-04-23|website=TenEighty|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://grmdaily.com/video/ksi-swarmz-tion-wayne-houdini|title=KSI, Swarmz & Tion Wayne Join Forces For Huge Single \"Houdini\"|last=|first=|date=2020-04-24|website=[[GRM Daily]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref> It was released on 24 April 2020 through [[RBC Records]], under [[BMG Rights Management]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.einpresswire.com/article/515167093/ksi-releases-new-single-houdini-featuring-swarmz-tion-wayne|title=KSI Releases New Single, \u201cHoudini\u201d Featuring Swarmz, Tion Wayne|date=2020-04-24|website=EIN Presswire|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref> It is the fourth single from KSI's upcoming 2020 debut album ''Dissimulation''.\n\n== Promotion ==\nOn 17 April 2020, KSI announced via social media that he would be releasing a new single on 24 April titled \"Houdini\", which features Swarmz and Tion Wayne, saying \"we about to drop the biggest U.K. banger of 2020\".<ref>{{Cite tweet|user=KSIOlajidebt|number=1251124441838428160|title=WE ABOUT TO DROP THE BIGGEST U.K. BANGER OF 2020. Houdini out next Friday. Pre order here|date=2020-04-17|access-date=2020-04-24|author=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B_FNa58ALGc/|title=\u201cWE ABOUT TO DROP THE BIGGEST U.K. BANGER OF 2020. Houdini out next Friday. Pre order link in bio \ud83d\udcf7: @kelvinjoness\u201d|last=KSI|first=|date=2020-04-17|website=[[Instagram]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref> The song was made available for [[pre-order]] on the same day.\n\n== Music video ==\nThe music video, directed by Kaylum, was filmed in [[London]] in March 2020 and was uploaded to KSI's YouTube channel on 24 April 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0iOSVD1fitU|title=KSI \u2013 Houdini (feat. Swarmz & Tion Wayne) [Official Music Video]|date=2020-04-24|website=[[YouTube]]|url-status=live|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2020/04/23/ksi-new-song-houdini-swarmz-tion-wayne-release-music-video-pictures-12593442/|title=KSI hangs out with Swarmz in stripped down music video for new single 'Houdini'|last=|first=|date=2020-04-23|website=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro]]|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref name=autogenerated2 />\n| length5 = \n| all_writing = \n| title2 = \n| length2 = \n| title3 = \n| length3 = \n| title4 = \n| length4 = \n| title5 = \n| title6 = \n| title7 = \n| title1 = Houdini\n| length7 = \n| title8 = \n| length8 = \n| title9 = \n| length9 = \n| title10 = \n| length10 = \n| length6 = \n| length1 = 2:49\n| note1 = featuring Swarmz and Tion Wayne\n| total_length = \n}}\n\n== Credits and personnel ==\nCredits adapted from [[Tidal (service)|Tidal]].<ref name=\"autogenerated1\">{{cite web|url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/136601853/credits|title=Houdini (feat. Swarmz & Tion Wayne) by KSI|date=2020-04-24|website=[[Tidal (service)|Tidal]]|url-status=live|accessdate=2020-04-24}}</ref>\n{{div col}}\n*[[KSI (entertainer)|KSI]] \u2013 vocals, songwriter\n*Swarmz \u2013 vocals, songwriter\n*Tion Wayne \u2013 vocals, songwriter\n*Eight9FLY \u2013 songwriter\n*Aj \u2013 producer, songwriter\n*Jacob \u2013 producer, songwriter\n*Henkka Niemist\u00f6 \u2013 engineer\n*Michalis Michael \u2013 engineer\n{{div col end}}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Region\n! scope=\"col\" |Date\n! scope=\"col\" |Format\n! scope=\"col\" |Label\n! scope=\"col\" |Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |Various\n| 24 April 2020\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| {{hlist|[[RBC Records|RBC]]|[[BMG Rights Management|BMG]]}}\n| <ref name=\"autogenerated2\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/gb/album/houdini-feat-swarmz-tion-wayne-single/1506840005|title=Houdini (feat. Swarmz & Tion 